  <brief_title>Effects of Lidocaine Spray for Reducing Pain During Endometrial Aspiration Biopsy : a Randomized Controlled Trial</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effects of Lidocaine Spray for Reducing Pain During Endometrial Aspiration Biopsy : a Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
